== 分集 ==
专题片共分八集：第一集《人心向背》；第二集《以上率下》；第三集《踏石留印》；第四集《利剑出鞘》；第五集《把纪律挺在前面》；第六集《拍蝇惩贪》；第七集《天网追逃》；第八集《标本兼治》<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1544501|title=专题片《永远在路上》今晚央视播出，采访苏荣等多位落马高官|accessdate=2016-10-18|date=2016-10-17|publisher=澎湃新闻|archive-date=2019-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811090536/http://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1544501|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20161023000625-260309|title=陸反腐片有節奏 預告追緝貪官|date=2016-10-23|newspaper=中時電子報|accessdate=2018-03-26|archive-date=2019-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111075603/https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20161023000625-260309|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第一集中首次曝光了疑似[[中华人民共和国公安部|公安部]][[秦城监狱|秦城监狱]]的内景。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.sohu.com/20161018/n470536775.shtml|title=《永远在路上》：周本顺李春城白恩培现身说法|accessdate=2016-10-18|date=2016-10-18|publisher=搜狐|archive-date=2019-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190111215143/http://news.sohu.com/20161018/n470536775.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

